<p>To a lesser extent, mez, mana recovery spells (to include necro mana pumps and mod rods) are also a problem that affect balance in a detrimental way.</p>

<p>Of course, if you take all that away, if your not careful you end up with a non-fun PoS game like SWG.</p>
