<p class="posted"><strong>Posted by <a href="mailto&#58;loral&#64;loralciriclight&#46;com">Loral</a> at October 13, 2004 11:03 AM</strong></p>
<p>"But neither Paladins or Necros are healers. So when you're looking at your choices for healers, the fact that other classes can rez only matters if you happen to have one of them along to do something else."</p>

