<p>You keep mentioning that a druid and a pally can be just as effective as a group with a cleric, which I find humorous, as a cleric can take any tank in the game, or in some cases even a pet class and do well.  You are certainly entitled to your opinion and to split hairs about calling it tuning instead of balance, or in saying talk about your own class not others, but EQ is about competition for group spots.  If they gave druids a 96 percent rez and gave no compensation to clerics, and then gave them a real CH for the cost you pay, I bet you'd be talking about class balance real quick... it's easy to say breathing's not a problem when you have the lone oxygen tank...</p>

